option1.title: Find the daily challenge
option1.desc: At 00:00 UTC, the problem will update at the top of the problem list. You have 24 hours to solve the problem.

option2.title: Submit your code
option2.desc: Earn 10 LeetCoins after an Accepted submission. A submission must be made again even if you have previously submitted an accepted code.

option3.title: Win a badge
option3.desc: After completing the entire LeetCoding Challenge for the month, earn additional LeetCoins and that months badge.

option1.title: Redeem TTT
option1.desc: Click on Redeem or visit LeetCode Store to redeem time travel ticket. Max: 3 tickets/ month.

option2.title: Find the missed problem
option2.desc: Click the date on calendar to submit code. Tickets are valid for all problems needed to be made up.

option3.title: Make up the problem
option3.desc: Submit an accepted code and confirm ticket usage. You can still earn the badge after using a ticket.

markGuideline.option1: 10 LeetCoins are rewarded immediately after accepted submission.
markGuideline.option2: For additional LeetCoins, please refer to this discuss post.
markGuideline.option3: Monthly LeetCoding Challenge Badge will be shown on the last day of the month after accepted submission.
markGuideline.option4: Users who completed all Daily LeetCoding Challenge non-premium problems for the month (with or without using Time Travel Tickets) will win a badge.
markGuideline.option5: With the Premium membership, you can submit an additional question each week. Once your submission is approved, you will receive 35 points.

remarkGuideline.option1: Tickets make up any invalid or late submission for all problems.
remarkGuideline.option2: Tickets are only valid through the end of the month in which they are redeemed.
remarkGuideline.option3: The redeem cycle ends at 23:00 on the last day of the month. Both times are based on UTC.
remarkGuideline.option4: After using time travel ticket to complete a problem, you can earn the 10 LeetCoins for completing the problem. However, youll not be qualified to earn additional LeetCoins for completing the entire challenge.
